headline: AEP Named One of America's Most JUST Companies for Fifth Consecutive Year
summary: American Electric Power (Nasdaq: AEP) has been named to the JUST 100 list for the fifth year in a row. This ranking by JUST Capital recognizes America's best corporate citizens. AEP placed in the top 20 for the third year in a row and received second place in the utilities industry.
